00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:34,520
No, wait, hang on, it's a funeral.

537
00:36:34,520 --> 00:36:36,840
Yeah, it should be a black bikini.

538
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:39,320
OK. Roll cameras...

